\par 
\par Status bar\tab Toggles the status bar on and off.
\par 
\par \{bmc font.bmp\}Font\tab Opens a font requester which determines the font to be used for the game text.
\par 
\par \{bmc options.bmp\}Options\tab Opens the }{\uldb options dialog}{\v options}{.
\par 
\par \{bmc scroll.bmp\}Scrollback\tab Opens the scrollback dialog, which shows all the text output by the interpreter. Using this dialog text can be copied into the clipboard.
\par }\pard\plain \s16\widctlpar\adjustright \fs20\lang2057\cgrid {\f1 
